title: Ep 232 - Jethalal Is Angry
shortDesc: Knowing that everyone has arranged an intervention for him for a wrong reason,  Jethalal gets angry. Later, he talks to his wife and asks her to trust him. They make it up together and convey their love for each other.

title: Ep 233 - Goli Sees Jethalal Getting A Haircut
shortDesc: Jethalal finally decides to get a haircut and ends up at a street barber's shop. Goli sees Jetha on the road and demands to reveal it to others. Later,  he loses his purse and gets caught with the police. How did all this happen?

title: Ep 234 - Karie Visits The Gadas
shortDesc: Jethalal's friend Karie decides to visits the Gada family. Daya gets excited to welcome her and decides to give her a grand welcome. Will Karie like the welcome? Watch the episode to find out.

title: Ep 235 - Karie Loves Gokuldham
shortDesc: Karie visits everyone at Gokuldham Society and loves the hospitality provided by the society members.

title: Ep 236 - Navaratri At Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: It is the first day of Navaratri and everyone at Gokuldham is excited. The ladies have decided to go shopping for Navaratri outfits. Will Karie be included as well? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 237 - Popatlal Has Fallen In Love
shortDesc: Navaratri is here and everyone at Gokuldham society is super excited to celebrate it together. Meanwhile, the ladies find out that Popatlal has a crush on Karie and Gada electronics comes up with a new Navratri Offer.

title: Ep 238 - Popatlals Demand
shortDesc: The ladies go shopping for Dandiya costumes along with Sundar and Karie.  They all at Ahmedabad when Popatlal calls Daya. He demands for the same coloured and patterned dress as Karie's. Will he be satisfied?

title: Ep 239 - Navaratri At Ahmedabad
shortDesc: The ladies decide to stay back at Ahmedabad for one more day to celebrate Navratri. They all dance and enjoy meanwhile, their husbands come all the way to Ahmedabad to bring them home.

title: Ep 240 - Popatlal Stuck In Ahmedabad
shortDesc: The members of the society return to Gokuldham Society return home from Ahmedabad. But, they realize that they've left Popatlal behind on the way.

title: Ep 241 - Jethalal Unhappy About Popatlals Crush
shortDesc: Hungover from Navaratri celebrations, Jethalal wakes up to a shocking news. Daya informs him that she thinks Popatlal has a crush on Karie. Hearing this makes Jethalal furious. How will he react?

title: Ep. 242 - Popatlal Gets A Makeover To Impress - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal seeks help from the ladies in the society, in regards to his love over Kerry. So they did have a conversation with Kerry to figure out the way for making Kerry fall in love with Popatlal. Hence they gave a makeover to Popatlal.

title: Ep. 243 - Popatlal's Disastrous Date With Kerry - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal and Kerry go to the park, he was struggling hard to keep up with his image in front of Kerry. But there were a lot of disturbances, and Kerry's handbag was snatched away by a petty thief. Popatlal tried to show his heroism for Kerry.

title: Ep 244 - Jethalal The Villain.
shortDesc: Jethalal, on his way to work, sees Popatlal being comforted by Karie. Later, Karie shares her happiness with Daya and does the Garba with her out of happiness.

title: Ep 245 - Jethalal And Diwali Games
shortDesc: Champaklal is talking to his friend on the phone and explaining to him how much times have changed. Later, he blesses his family members to live a long and a prosperous life.

title: Ep 246 - Ajay Devgan Visits The Gadas
shortDesc: Jethalal and Daya have a miscommunication and forget to bring him home from Gada electronics. Ajay Devgan runs into Champaklal and drops him home. What happens next?
